name: Haunted Helmet
description:
A Rider on motorcycle: (Driving Fast in the tunnel) I been Driving in this tunnel for 30 Minutes why hasn't it Ended?
(Runs out of petrol) Guess I have to wait for someone to help maybe a car will pass by soon....
(Sudden noise) LOOK OVER HERE!
Biker: Hello is someone there? ( Saw a helmet laying on the floor)
Biker: The helmet looks good someone must have dropped it Here 
(Helmet suddenly attach itself to the biker An-)
